  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime aerial view of a sprawling city illuminated with countless lights. The cityscape stretches across the horizon, creating a vibrant orange glow that transitions into a deep, dark blue sky above. A long, hazy comet streaks across the upper portion of the image, appearing as a bright white line. Silhouetted trees frame the left side of the image, adding depth and a natural element to the urban scene. The city lights are dense and appear to be from residential and commercial areas. The overall composition conveys a sense of scale and wonder.",
